title: Musicians: Leave Your Ego at the Door
description:
Saxophonist, teacher, and music legend Gary Bartz discusses the importance of leaving your ego at the door anytime you get ready to play music.

Learn more by visiting the Jazz Academy at http://academy.jazz.org
